OL,3,CPub staff 'attacked' as thieves target
OL,4,Cbarrels of used cooking oil
OL,6,FPubs and restaurants are being warned
OL,7,Fabout a rising number of barrels of
OL,8,Fcooking oil being stolen.
OL,10,FThieves are targeting the barrels,
OL,11,Fwhich are either being stored for use
OL,12,Fin the future or are full of used oil,
OL,13,Fand often pose as legitimate
OL,14,Fcollectors.
OL,16,FWayne Childs, landlord of the Kings
OL,17,FArms in , Gloucestershire, said: "It
OL,18,Fis a massive problem, we've had to up
OL,19,Four security massively.
