OL,6,F"We've had to buy an oil safe
OL,7,Fbasically to store our waste oil now
OL,8,Fbecause we've had gates damaged and
OL,9,FI've had staff assaulted."
OL,11,FPub owners say the barrels themselves
OL,12,Fcan be worth several hundred pounds.
OL,14,FGloucestershire Police say the thieves
OL,15,Foften arrive in vans where they can
OL,16,Fstore large drums in the rear of the
OL,17,Fvehicle.
