OL,6,FMr Childs told ITV News West Country:
OL,7,F"They're turning it into biodiesel,
OL,8,Fwe've got a licensed company from
OL,9,FBirmingham that comes and collects our
OL,10,Fwaste oil.
OL,12,F"At present day we get 30p a litre and
OL,13,Fthat can go up to 60p sometimes, so it
OL,14,Fgets processed by proper companies,
OL,15,Fbut the oil thieves are doing it
OL,16,Fillegally."
