OL,10,Foil barrels are a waste product and
OL,11,Fnot covered by insurance.
OL,13,FMr Childs said: "Obviously we don't
OL,14,Fsee the money coming back and we've
OL,15,Fseen hospitality trade struggling so
OL,16,Fmuch, which is a present.
